section.invoiceRules:
(1) For a single invoice under ¥200, only an e-invoice PDF is required;
(2) For ¥200 or more, manually enter actual payment amount based on payment records and upload payment records (multiple allowed); if it differs from the invoice amount, explain why;
(3) If item names are vague (e.g. components, batch, set) or lack specific names/quantities, check the box and upload a purchase list;
(4) If the issuer and payee differ, check the box and upload an explanation.
